column10: dig_threshold_desc:I used this strategy for all BUT block 1 of the game.
column16: other_desc:Basically I estimated that it took 4 digs to equate to leaving the planet and starting a dig on another. So I began to estimate in my head whether or not the next 4 digs on this planet would add up to the first dig (which I knew would hover around 100 gems) on a new planet. If the answer was no
column17: then I left. This strategy kicked in mostly in the last two or three blocks.
column18: feedback:Just a small suggestion! Maybe we could be shown a counter of how many gems we've tallied
column19: and some sort of metric for understanding how it equates to bonus. It's just a fun incentive to have as we go along the game.}
